---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';

const title = 'Privacy Policy | Calc and Measure';
const description = 'How Calc and Measure uses cookies, Google AdSense, and analytics, explained in plain language.';
const path = '/privacy-policy/';
const lastUpdated = 'July 7, 2026';

const schema = {
  '@type': 'BreadcrumbList',
  itemListElement: [
    { '@type': 'ListItem', position: 1, name: 'Home', item: 'https://calcandmeasure.com/' },
    { '@type': 'ListItem', position: 2, name: 'Privacy Policy', item: 'https://calcandmeasure.com/privacy-policy/' },
  ],
};
---

<BaseLayout title={title} description={description} path={path} schema={schema}>
  <nav class="breadcrumbs" aria-label="Breadcrumb">
    <a href="/">Home</a>
    <span class="sep">&gt;</span>
    <span aria-current="page">Privacy Policy</span>
  </nav>

  <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
  <p class="disclaimer">Last updated: {lastUpdated}</p>

  <p>
    This page explains what data Calc and Measure collects, why, and how you can control it.
    We have kept it in plain language rather than dense legal text.
  </p>

  <h2>What This Site Does Not Do</h2>
  <p>
    Every calculator and converter on this site runs entirely in your browser. Values you type
    into a tool, like a date of birth, a bill amount, or a course grade, are never sent to a
    server, stored in a database, or seen by anyone else. There is no account system and
    nothing to sign up for.
  </p>

  <h2>Cookies</h2>
  <p>
    This site uses cookies for two purposes: to remember whether you have accepted or declined
    the cookie notice, and to support the advertising described below. Your browser lets you
    block or delete cookies at any time through its settings, though doing so may cause the
    cookie banner to reappear on your next visit.
  </p>

  <h2>Google AdSense</h2>
  <p>
    This site shows ads served by Google AdSense. Google and its advertising partners may use
    cookies and similar technologies to show ads based on your visits to this site and other
    sites, in order to make ads more relevant to you. You can learn more about how Google uses
    data from sites that use its services, and adjust your ad personalization settings, at
    Google's <a href="https://policies.google.com/technologies/partner-sites" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Ads and data</a> page.
  </p>
  <p>
    Visitors in the European Economic Area and the United Kingdom are shown a consent banner
    that lets you choose whether to allow personalized advertising, in line with Google's
    certified consent requirements for those regions.
  </p>

  <h2>Advertising Cookies and Your Choices</h2>
  <p>
    Calc and Measure uses Google AdSense to show ads, and Google and other third party
    advertising vendors use cookies to serve ads based on a visitor's prior visits to this
    site and to other sites across the web. This is sometimes called interest based or
    personalized advertising. It works by tracking browsing patterns at the browser or device
    level, not by identifying who you are.
  </p>
  <p>
    This advertising data does not include personal identifiers such as your name, home
    address, or email address. Google's own explanation of how it and its partners handle
    data collected on sites like this one is available at
    <a href="https://policies.google.com/technologies/partner-sites" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">policies.google.com/technologies/partner-sites</a>.
  </p>
  <p>
    If you would prefer not to see personalized ads, you can adjust your settings directly
    with Google at <a href="https://adssettings.google.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Google Ad Settings</a>,
    or use the industry wide opt-out tool provided by the Digital Advertising Alliance at
    <a href="https://www.aboutads.info" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">aboutads.info</a>.
    Both let you opt out of interest based advertising across many participating sites and
    advertisers, not just this one.
  </p>
  <p>
    You can also disable cookies entirely through your browser's settings, which applies to
    the cookies used for advertising as well as the ones this site uses to remember your
    cookie banner choice. Doing so may cause some site features, such as remembering that
    choice between visits, to stop working as expected.
  </p>

  <h2>Analytics</h2>
  <p>
    This site may use a privacy-conscious analytics tool to understand overall traffic, such as
    which pages are visited and roughly how many people visit, so the site can be improved. Any
    analytics used here does not identify you personally and is separate from the advertising
    cookies described above.
  </p>

  <h2>Children's Privacy</h2>
  <p>
    This site is not directed at children under 13 and does not knowingly collect personal
    information from them.
  </p>

  <h2>Changes to This Policy</h2>
  <p>
    If this policy changes, the updated version will be posted on this page with a new "last
    updated" date at the top.
  </p>

  <h2>Contact</h2>
  <p>
    Questions about this policy can be sent to
    <a href="mailto:contact@calcandmeasure.com">contact@calcandmeasure.com</a>.
  </p>
</BaseLayout>
